messages.text: You know me. Pulling up now though.
Is today a special day or something?
Just one other car in the parking lot
Weird, that place is usually packed
It’s pickup time, they have to be, they’re religious about it
Hold on let me re-check the calendar
Any chance they’re on a field trip?
OK will look around but this place isn’t big
OK I’ll call Susan to see if she picked up Dylan
Susan was incredibly rude to me
She just said “stay away” and “keep your child”
No, about to check the bathrooms
There’s a message on the bathroom window
Babe now I’m really freakin worried
It’s from the Bible I think
OK I am going to leave work and head home
OK I’ll hang here for a bit and look around some more
You said there was another car there, right?
I think it’s Meg’s, the head teacher
I’m about 5mins away from the house
Maybe they took the kids all home or something
Car was a mess and there was some concerning stuff in it
Concerning? Felix you need to be more specific right now
No I’m actually getting out of the car in front of the house
Well…I don’t know how to say this but…
Meg had books on ritual sacrifices in her backseat
OMG we need to find Max right now! Felix!
I’ll call the management of this place
Did you leave the door to our place open when you left?
But what if Max is in there?
What if MEG is in there with him?
All the more reason for me going in
Besides, how did she get here if her car is there?
Place is fine, except for Max’s room
Smells like something was burned in here
Almost looks like a bonfire was had on the carpet in his room
Good thing the whole place didn’t burn down
Something scrawled on the floor too, hold on
She took him to Blake Park, his favorite place to play
Sitting cross-legged in the park, her back is to me
I tried to talk to her
She…had another small child in her arms
It looked really bad, maybe dead
I asked and she pointed to the woods nearby
OMG Ok I am a few mins away
I am at the spot she pointed to
OMG I hear screaming from under the dirt
I know you feel bad about going back to work after what happened
But I just want you to know that I’m fine staying home with Max
Still just staring out the window
What happened to our little boy Felix? Why did Meg bury him alive?
Why did she kill all those other kids and not our boy?
I don’t know and don’t want to think about it
She’s away now and Max is safe
Yeah but all of those other families, our friends
I know but, will Max ever recover?
What?? He’s finally talking again? What is he saying?
He’s just rocking himself saying “Finish for Meg” over and over
OK I’m coming back home now
The grave is so much deeper now, you won’t find him
